        "type": "object",
        "description": "Please note, fileAI system has a naming convention for certain line items' columns ([see naming convention](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/11xI8bPiK1c6XWzOadbiiHfUeDqGqbdb7vZhjXHmMvNg/edit?usp=sharing))",
